WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:15.218 --> 00:00:16.749
Yes, please?

00:00:16.956 --> 00:00:20.076
Lady: Is awakening ever accompanied
by fear?

00:00:20.277 --> 00:00:21.592
Lady translator: Pardon?

00:00:21.793 --> 00:00:24.470
Other lady: Is awakening never accompanied
by fear?

00:00:24.671 --> 00:00:26.972
Lady: Is it ever accompanied, I said.
Other lady: Ever.

00:00:27.173 --> 00:00:30.847
Lady translator: Is awakening ever
accompanied by fear?

00:00:31.048 --> 00:00:35.107
Shri Mataji: No. Never. I mean, people
have given you

00:00:35.308 --> 00:00:42.077
such horrible books about Kundalini,
I’m Myself shocked.

00:00:57.596 --> 00:01:03.910
When I read about it, I could not
understand what are they up to.

00:01:09.455 --> 00:01:12.789
But supposing say, you put your fingers
in the plug

00:01:12.990 --> 00:01:17.426
and then you say “I got a shock”,

00:01:22.935 --> 00:01:29.976
one would say that, that was, that means
you do not know how to handle electricity.

00:01:31.661 --> 00:01:35.880
But it is much more than that.

00:01:36.521 --> 00:01:42.406
If a person who raises the Kundalini has
the authority from the Divine,

00:01:42.607 --> 00:01:48.744
it will never, never harm, whatever way
he tries.

00:02:02.348 --> 00:02:08.495
But such a person himself has to be a pure
person.

00:02:11.462 --> 00:02:17.330
If such a person is interested in your
money and in your purse,

00:02:19.508 --> 00:02:23.581
then it has nothing to do with God.

00:02:23.782 --> 00:02:31.630
You cannot purchase it, you cannot purchase
God or Divine,

00:02:31.831 --> 00:02:35.864
you cannot pay for it.

00:02:36.947 --> 00:02:39.638
So those people I think, who have tried
I mean,

00:02:39.839 --> 00:02:44.533
really sinister to do such a harm
to people.

00:02:55.706 --> 00:03:02.401
Of course in some people it does not rise
that fast.

00:03:05.310 --> 00:03:08.293
If you have problems, say if you have
liver problems,

00:03:08.494 --> 00:03:15.215
then Kundalini will go and show
the pulsation at that point.

00:03:27.156 --> 00:03:37.057
And some people who have been to wrong
type of gurus, or wrong type of cults,

00:03:47.471 --> 00:03:53.352
may behave in a way that is very funny
sometimes.

00:03:55.196 --> 00:03:58.769
We have had very funny experiences say
for T.M. people,

00:03:58.970 --> 00:04:02.949
if they are sitting before Me and I try
to awaken their Kundalini

00:04:03.150 --> 00:04:06.826
they start jumping on their seats.

00:04:22.309 --> 00:04:28.567
Not all but some did, for a while,

00:04:28.768 --> 00:04:32.297
but then they settled down.

00:04:33.900 --> 00:04:42.332
And some people who are called as orange
people, also start jumping a little bit.

00:04:48.705 --> 00:04:53.478
It happens, a little reaction comes to some
people.

00:04:54.482 --> 00:05:03.076
But doesn’t matter, as long as you are
attentive, it works out, it soothes down.

00:05:14.802 --> 00:05:20.197
Sometimes people feel little heat
on the hands,

00:05:21.928 --> 00:05:26.442
specially if you have a liver problem.

00:05:27.113 --> 00:05:31.209
And when the Kundalini comes out, She first
throws away little heat from your head,

00:05:31.410 --> 00:05:35.007
not much, but little heat.

00:05:39.656 --> 00:05:44.986
But ultimately cool breeze starts coming
out of your head,

00:05:48.976 --> 00:05:54.344
and you feel the cool breeze moving
from your hand also.

00:06:02.392 --> 00:06:05.890
But you need not worry, we know all
the permutations and combinations

00:06:06.091 --> 00:06:09.488
of these complications.

00:06:16.289 --> 00:06:19.250
Yes.

00:06:19.451 --> 00:06:22.602
Question [translated by lady translator]:
By which way… What is the means…

00:06:22.803 --> 00:06:25.181
Shri Mataji: By which way…
Lady translator: …of awakening Kundalini?

00:06:25.382 --> 00:06:31.414
Shri Mataji: That’s a good thing. I’ll just
tell you after we start. Eh?

